- **Analyze Jonah and Twin Earth cases for achievement-verb structure.** Conduct fine-grained linguistic/semantic analysis of why Jonah (false descriptive content about identity) and Twin Earth (natural-kind extension) do not contain the same achievement-verb bifurcation as Gödel. Map onto psycholinguistic predictions about what should trigger brute-fact vs. social-fact parsing.

