- **Nisbett's holistic/analytic framework**: Case-specificity is inconsistent with a global cognitive style difference. If holistic thought were the driver, it should flatten responses across all cases equally.

- **Simple presupposition-ambiguity hypothesis**: Clarifying presuppositions in the vignette (Sytsma & Livengood 2011) does not eliminate the effect. The mechanism operates downstream of presupposition clarity.

